body_html: I'm a part of a group of 4 students from Drexel University who are currently working on this. Because we are not very familiar with tensorflow we are going to start by implementing tf.argument() directly as a kernel without a GPU kernel. After we get that we are going to try to implement atan, as implemented by eigen, and then making the tf.argument function a composition. Let us know if you have any tips, advice, or feedback.
